OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FA football fan has been sentenced to
OL,8,Fnine months in prison and banned from
OL,9,Fmatches for six years after admitting
OL,10,Fracially abusing a Forest Green Rovers
OL,11,Ffootball player.
OL,13,FRyan Ferguson, from Liverpool, shouted
OL,14,Fwhat's been described as 'horrific and
OL,15,Fviolent' abuse at forward Jordon
OL,16,FGarrick at the New Lawn in April 2023.
OL,18,FHe's one of the first people in the
OL,19,Fcountry to be jailed for such an
OL,20,Foffence.
