OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FGarrick said he was shaken by the
OL,8,Fincident and the language used were
OL,9,F'words no one should have to hear'.
OL,11,FCCTV captured the Ferguson's diatribe,
OL,12,Fdelivered just minutes before he was
OL,13,Fescorted out of the stands by security.
OL,15,FHe was then questioned by police where
OL,16,Fhe gave false details before being
OL,17,Farrested. It later emerged he already
OL,18,Fhad five-year football banning order,
OL,19,Fimposed in 2019.
