OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Garrick said: "I
OL,8,Fwas shocked at the words used against
OL,9,Fme and they are words no one should
OL,10,Fhave to ever hear."
OL,12,FArriving at court today Ferguson had
OL,13,Fbeen warned to expect a prison
OL,14,Fsentence - one of the first cases in
OL,15,Fthe country where a football fan has
OL,16,Fbeen jailed for abusing a player.
OL,18,FPC Adrian Tuft, of Gloucestershire
OL,19,FPolice, said: "It supports the work
OL,20,Fthat we're doing in trying to tackle
OL,21,Fracism within football.
